race.comment: BLUE CABANG (3) steps out for the first time at this track. Comes here after a last start 4th and beaten 6 lengths (19.62) at Healesville. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Has ability and looks hard to stop. MIDNIGHT STAR (6) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by one length at this track in a handy 22.99 beating History's Coming. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Has definite claims. IMPRESS LUCKIE (7) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (23.34) last time in a Mix 1/2/3 at this track. Form at the trip sound including 11 wins. Likely to be about the money. DOUBLE THREAT (1) has claims fresh from a recent placing at big odds.
